{"tid":511311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼父用性玩具狎玩女兒 影淫照上傳網上","createTime":"2017-12-27T11:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T03:03:09.000Z","uid":35468,"like":75,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"f27077f2fb60a98e0da36d23d97f5f4af08aa27f","tid":511311,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T11:03:50.000Z","msg":"獸父拿情趣用品性侵高中女兒　拍裸照傳雲端<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20171225/1265681/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20171225%2F1265681%2F&d=68iVoqjodNF3NsX5NqndSMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a3eec33b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20171225%2F1265681%2F&h=2b928775\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20171225/1265681/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171225/640_1b12d353c5b803a4d38fb626557148e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171225%2F640_1b12d353c5b803a4d38fb626557148e9.jpg&h=d7e32beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高雄1名擁有碩士學歷的狼父，被控猥褻就讀高中的愛女，3次以情趣用品性侵女兒，還強脫女兒衣褲檢查身體，甚至拍裸照上傳雲端。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，判決指出，狼父從2016年4月女兒升上高一之後，以要多了解彼此身體為由，將女兒壓制在床上強脫衣物猥褻。狼父至少3次以買來的情趣用品，性侵女兒，還拿手機拍下女兒的裸照上傳雲端硬碟。<br />\n<br />\n法院審理時，狼父一度否認，後來才坦承犯行。法官認為被告為被害人生父，竟未克制自己性衝動，為滿足一己色慾，違反倫常，對於女兒身心造成難以抹滅之傷痛，依強制猥褻、性侵少女等罪判狼父18年。"},{"pid":"2ef1f5479d3db98749c41edd78af419ff9ee6b83","tid":511311,"uid":82532,"like":280,"dislike":7,"score":273,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T11:04:47.000Z","msg":"真係人神共憤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 究竟up咗去邊"},{"pid":"ebda4c89b713b7b4d446a6ac6a623e4022141bac","tid":511311,"uid":25858,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係人神共憤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 究竟up咗去邊</bloc